A more direct analog of plot(BodyWeight) would be

xyplot(BodyWeight, weight ~ Time | Rat,
       aspect = "xy", type = "o",
       groups = Diet, auto.key = list(title = "Diet", columns = 3),
       grid = TRUE, xlab = labs[1], ylab = labs[2])

